{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"e94e0d7d-726d-4ff0-83a7-d9721531a69f","content":"Your `.testsettings` file is a **legacy format** that modern MSTest (v3+) ignores. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how each setting maps:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout=30000` | `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Assembly resolution / deployment | `<DeploymentEnabled>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Code coverage data collector | `<DataCollector>` in `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |\n\nLet me create the `.runsettings` file and wire it up in your project:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01Euay9WWFHyhUQE4ExuQqdh","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Migrating test settings"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01TbT1UWGrSpB4DVhwmkYJwQ","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-c37bad33a8eb4590a15729a3b3b35a17/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-c37bad33a8eb4590a15729a3b3b35a17/local.runsettings."},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01DNR8inc4it2xREJzJm14Qu","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-c37bad33a8eb4590a15729a3b3b35a17/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"  <PropertyGroup>\n  